## Privacy Policy
W&P treats personal data seriously.  While we do not collect personally identifying information from visitors to this site unless this information is directly provided by the visitor or through the visitor’s browser,  the only personally identifying information we collect and/or store is the information you provide to us when you e-mail us or use our online contact form. W&P will not use information provided through your use of this site except to communicate via email, respond to direct inquiries and/or to measure and analyze website traffic. The information that is collected will not be provided or sold to third parties. W&P reserves the right to change this Privacy Policy at any time, without advanced warning to users of our site. Should any new policy go into effect, W&P will post it on this site. Any new policy will not be retroactive.
